                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 817.51/1002</note>
                <head ana="#head_untitled-inferred-from-preceding-sibling-head">[Untitled]</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1917-09-18T15:00:00-05:45">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 18, 1917, 3 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Department’s September 12, 5 p.m.<note n="6" xml:id="d1381fn6">Not
                        printed.</note> In addition to note of Minister for Foreign Affairs reported
                    in my September 12, 3 p.m., authorizing Enriquez to represent Nicaragua, I have
                    obtained and have in my possession in legal form power of attorney authorizing
                    him to arrange and conclude agreements with the bankers. Will forward this
                    document by first pouch.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jefferson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
